Supporting Assault
Survivors Together

At AlertShe, we believe in the power of connection and community. Our online platform offers a safe space for women in emergency situations to communicate with each other and share experiences. We also provide resources for sexual assault victims, empowering them to seek help, connect with others, and heal. Our mission is to help those in need and create a supportive network that will encourage growth and recovery.

Our Core Initiatives

Empowering change for a brighter tomorrow

Find your Community

At Alert She, we believe that healing and progress come from sharing and connecting with others, which is why we have created a platform for survivors to come together and build a community of support. Our safe and secure, blockchain-encrypted website offers a space for individuals to share their stories and experiences without fear of judgement or stigma. By joining Alert She, you'll have access to a welcoming, supportive community of survivors who understand what you're going through.

Report Emergency 

We understand the importance of staying safe and connected in today's fast-paced world. Our quick-send alert button feature allows you to notify your emergency contacts with a single click, streamlining the process of contacting your loved ones and the required personnel when you need help fast. Whether you're running errands or just going about your day, have peace of mind knowing that your loved ones are just a button press away.

Women Safe Zones

Our goal is to create a community that prioritizes and supports the welfare of women. At Alert She, we also provide our users with information on women-friendly areas and businesses. With our map and list views, we make it easy for you to find businesses that prioritize the safety and comfort of women along with user reviews and ratings so you can make informed decisions. 

Resources and Safety Tips

We are committed to providing information on safety measures, legal rights and self-defense. Our regular updates and access to reliable information make us an essential resource for women that seek to take control of their lives. Our content is sourced from trusted and reliable sources and is geared towards helping women take charge of their safety and well-being.

Articles and Resources 

Explore our collection of handpicked articles and other resources to keep you informed and safe.

Our team of experts is passionate about keeping people safe and informed, and we strive to provide our community with reliable, up-to-date information about women’s safety.


Our articles and resources are regularly updated, handpicked from the most reputable sources and designed to help women feel confident and empowered in their daily lives. Join us today and become a part of our safe and supportive community.

Our Story

AlertShe was founded by a group of dedicated individuals passionate about women's safety and technology. Inspired by the need for a trustworthy platform where women can report incidents and access safety resources without fear of tampering, we created AlertShe. By leveraging blockchain technology, we aim to provide a secure space for women to share their experiences and support each other.
